{"tid":1651284,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"3.32億英鎊！曼聯工資總額成為英超歷史最高","createTime":"2019-10-13T09:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T15:51:34.000Z","uid":173952,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ccffa050c2b422ea1e9ee9f17ebd14b3035a9c3d","tid":1651284,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"據知名足球經濟博主Swiss Ramble消息，曼聯成為英超工資總額最多的球隊，達到了驚人的3.32億英鎊，這也是英超歷史上工資總額的最高紀錄。<br />\n過去三個賽季，曼聯的工資總額增長超過了1億英鎊，上個賽季，紅魔全隊的總工資是2.96億英鎊。<br />\n目前曼聯陣中工資較高的球員有：週薪37.5萬英鎊的德赫亞，週薪29萬英鎊的博格巴，週薪25萬英鎊的馬夏爾和周薪40萬英鎊的桑切斯（本賽季租借至國際米蘭）。<br />\n儘管擁有英超最高的薪水，但新賽季曼聯戰績糟糕，聯賽8輪戰罷，曼聯2勝3平3負僅積9分排在第12位。"},{"pid":"af4af3d809169f0f5f44e14f3ede27830f713602","tid":1651284,"uid":64600,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"排第一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beab5ebe410e3884a12ea4263d22dc11dc26f8a9","tid":1651284,"uid":87272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"仲有c朗筆錢"},{"pid":"1567e94abf57101269ccf23f4c5a824816ae5f86","tid":1651284,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"多謝雲爺爺黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbfd8adf1528612f11fbfaf7fe4238f4d51d6d2","tid":1651284,"uid":234309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1567e94abf57101269ccf23f4c5a824816ae5f86","tid":1651284,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"多謝雲爺爺黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"人不在，遺計仍在<img src=\"/assets/faces